changelog.change_log:
Added:
- Implemented support for new sites;
- Added new UI animations;
- Changed the design of the settings panel;
- Added a change of environment:
Now you can change the environment from 3 options: Room, Dark and Void!
- Changed the logic of the search at Web page:
Now to update the video list you need to confirm the request by pressing the enter button;

Fixed:
- Fixed AB mode operation when switching videos;
- Fixed launch of a random video when viewing a WebView
- Fixed incorrect video viewing date on the HISTORY page
